---
title: Crumbed Haloumi Burger & BBQ-Cherry Sauce with Kumara Wedges & Creamy Slaw
description: Sometimes a burger is the only thing that will satisfy! Try this new twist on a classic, with golden-crumbed haloumi drizzled in a BBQ-cherry sauce that’s the perfect combination of fruity and tangy.
